{"tid":1355210,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［反送中千載難逢機會］724香港大球場曼城訪港呀！","createTime":"2019-07-23T09:19:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-23T12:57:09.000Z","uid":196445,"like":28,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"9d6e9b441ebb3c2d584554d3b51d65c9c1a7a02d","tid":1355210,"uid":196445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T09:19:17.000Z","msg":"難得千載難逢機會，曼城將會喺香港時間7月24號 8:00對傑志， 難得同國際求救嘅好時機，有冇買飛呀巴打都去現場。<br />\n<br />\n首先建議全場着黑衫入場，反映香港人不會害怕 <br />\n<br />\n另外 比賽第21分鐘，全場會唱do you hear the people sing（已經廣傳咗）有冇有printer嘅巴打可以派歌詞<br />\n<br />\n最後場內嘅球迷有幾個建議可以做 <br />\n1:boo傑志 boo到完場<br />\n2:比賽尾聲或者結束之後衝入球場<br />\n3:比賽途中發出SOS求救訊號<br />\n4唱sing hallelujah to the lord <br />\n<br />\n冇飛嘅巴打可以做下文宣，或者喺球場外叫下口號"},{"pid":"3cc5367a5890a6f949cf12e6ce5e4ddc17f867c2","tid":1355210,"uid":196445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T09:20:05.000Z","msg":"有冇文宣巴打可以設計poster?"},{"pid":"ed23e65b0c8150952a02694e7f9999ec875283d7","tid":1355210,"uid":196445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T09:21:50.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad7cb0b1d19ba16385b87c321c7969cf52b1e50b","tid":1355210,"uid":125029,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T09:22:53.000Z","msg":"圍村地圖APP<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1354665\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1354665</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n幫手推上熱門 share 比出嚟元朗嘅人睇"},{"pid":"092b41ab4f99daeee747935a6a9a6c7f34a41b01","tid":1355210,"uid":63927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T09:23:29.000Z","msg":"Sing hallelujah to the lord"},{"pid":"c14f32ca3b6918d451c54fb49df9fd7a77ef5013","tid":1355210,"uid":196445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T09:24:39.000Z","msg":"推呀<img src=\"/assets/face